c: 33
v: 33
t: "Ne mwikhale mutsinzu tsienyu, ne mulechesia oburone bwenyu shingala bechesinja abakhasi betsinyanga tsiobusilu tawe, ne mulumilile okhulaama ne murusie eshihanwa, ne muwulile Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, Nyasaye yenya okhuba yiniakhwo eshifwolo enywe Abandu beyinzu, nende okhubatswenula muno"